tmjpad (0.1.1-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * First .deb-packaged release.
  * Fixes the v1.2 ISO icon-cache miss: postinst now runs
    gtk-update-icon-cache so the dedicated TMJPad icon (book +
    colored T/M/J letters) renders instead of falling back to the
    generic TMJOs logo.
  * No code changes vs the v1.2 in-ISO version — same Find/Replace,
    same persistence, same focus-on-tab behavior.

 -- TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>  Sun, 10 May 2026 17:45:00 -0300

tmjpad (0.1.0-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Initial release as part of TMJOs v1.2 ISO (in-ISO install via
    customize.sh, not yet a .deb). This entry documents the first
    public release of TMJPad.
  * Full session persistence with atomic writes.
  * Multiple tabs, Find & Replace, dark theme.

 -- TMJOs Team <tmjos-archive@tmjsistemas.com.br>  Sun, 10 May 2026 12:00:00 -0300
